text: Renesse, Zeelandic: Renisse, is a seaside resort in the Netherlands, and also a former municipality. The village belongs to the municipality of Schouwen- Duiveland in the province of Zeeland. In 2017, about 1,520 people lived in Renesse. == Other websites == * Website of Renesse Category:20th-century disestablishments in the Netherlands Category:Settlements in Zeeland Category:Former municipalities of Zeeland Category:Schouwen-Duiveland
